{
  "stem": "1860.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is-- there was always a spark of hope, no matter what.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe because I was so young, but always hopeful that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] things would somehow work themselves out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, it was a-- a tremendous comfort that I was all the time with my mother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm trying to think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We know-- don't know even exactly what-- when they left-- when Italy became close to introducing the anti-Semitic-- the-- the Nazi laws.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then my-- my father and my brother went-- left for Tangier, for North Africa, Tangier in Morocco.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we know-- we knew that much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we were so, so busy with-- with our own life that everything else-- we knew they are safe.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there was no other forms of communication, letters--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For a while, we used to get some letters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then it stopped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In ghetto, I'm trying to-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] well, there were-- there was a punishment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were the actions, the resettlements.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- when people were taken with transports there was one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In June, the one that we were going out to Optima, then there was a big one in October where many people were sent out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And trying to--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But these guards then at the time were mostly just to watch your comings and goings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the Krakow ghetto-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] trying to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm a little bit confused with the dates.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I am working at Optima.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then when Plaszow was formed, we-- we-- we were working-- we were-- we were moved to the camp in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We took our belongings, but whatever we could carry in our-- in two valises.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
